{"tid":341933,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"歌頌耶穌！讚美上帝！？","createTime":"2017-07-31T08:08:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-31T10:42:36.000Z","uid":108831,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bddef83be7ca64e3cf726820d6232c3b70dc9724","tid":341933,"uid":108831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:08:49.000Z","msg":"就奇呀屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 頂你個肺大家千祈咪撚惹耶撚真係好可怕，之前行街買野突然有幾個大學生話做訪問，見得閒咪幫佢地做下，問埋晒啲關於人生既問題搞到我以為佢地真係做學術研究，仲話有野要繼續問所以留左聯絡方式比佢地。<br />\n結果下次約我食飯，屌佢老母黎料，傾傾下問我有冇信仰，開始講上帝耶穌，講到依家已經幾個月，一個星期約我出黎食飯講經一次，好撚想死<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但佢地又好熱心咁樣我又唔識拒絕人，次次焗住出黎聽聖經聽撚到就黎訓著<br />\n其實之前已經瀨過一次野，有人上門禁鐘傳教唔識拒絕聽左十幾分鐘，結果後來每日都上門搵我，點解自己會咁蠢..<br />\n有冇巴絲試過比人咁樣煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 可唔可以教下我要點樣禮貌地拒絕佢地，大家見到咁樣幫你地做問卷既人記得say no<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 唔好好似我咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4417c977d17e165e783c270a257843d91e70d16d","tid":341933,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:12:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e94deffb1f22de4e0f9b2eb9d69d05b1ab61b06b","tid":341933,"uid":99364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:14:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"478d0d21bf215429dd71d17d9d8196bc637fdca9","tid":341933,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:14:32.000Z","msg":"直接叫佢唔洗再搵你 怕乜拒絕"},{"pid":"b5090f36e4c15eda8e5f28d8ebde3d5da94b08d0","tid":341933,"uid":23170,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-31T08:18:49.000Z","msg":"佢地有無請食飯定aa<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b212ac3bd999ad956a931b724df742365c0afb1f","tid":341933,"uid":22719,"like":0,"dislike